title: Vego Salad Bar - St 294
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Salad bar, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fish is the only meat, otherwise food is veg. Second location of this salad and wraps, sandwiches and juice restaurant. No fish sauce used. Build-your-own salad with choice of greens plus other ingredients, condiment, and dressing. Has free Wi-Fi.
